{"tid":1738074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對內文宣，你我有責","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:07:28.000Z","uid":111007,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"efb0a89e167f5989c0ee962de74f29f2f047df31","tid":1738074,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"圍魏救趙，反攻甚至救寶計劃一直都有Team做緊<br />\n我大聲同你地班仆街講！由六月到而家仲走到出黎既人已經有一定醒覺！<br />\n最嬲既係搞完一整日出返黎，見到你地互屌分化割蔗<br />\n你地真係對得住一班手足？<br />\n由其是班街都冇出過去既冷氣軍師，我唔知你地屌人既心態係為刷存在感定係有其實原因<br />\n<br />\n但入得黎呢個ＰＯＳＴ既手人今日同我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住一樣野</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足出去唔係為左俾你地屌同割蔗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">士氣同人數一樣緊要</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我宣報，由今日起除左要做對外文宣<br />\n仲要做埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對內文宣</span></span></strong>，加返大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">士氣值</span></strong>同建立返手足之間<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">信任度</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n放低張對內文宣，如果你地認為可行就幫手Share同推俾更多人知<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVSqbys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVSqbys.jpg&h=f91c55d4&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9b92138bf603bcc7851e47ed0ab0073dbcffe27a","tid":1738074,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82347b5f4eafe9b773f582ab4d583c4b524853a5","tid":1738074,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cc2d8300beb7ef64965b258c3c886ee2fcb7107c","tid":1738074,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f864f00769fff47605416ef8d37a00a29818d5f5